        Spawns a particle into the world with the given attributes, which can be configured further with the returned class Particle

        Parameters:
        particle - the name of the particle to spawn, see getParticleNames
        x - the x coordinate to spawn the particle at
        y - the y coordinate to spawn the particle at
        z - the z coordinate to spawn the particle at
        xSpeed - the motion the particle should have in the x direction
        ySpeed - the motion the particle should have in the y direction
        zSpeed - the motion the particle should have in the z direction
        Returns:
        the newly spawned particle for further configuration
        See Also:
        class Particle
